title: Faber-Castell Paint by Number Museum Series Vincent Van Gogh Sunflowers Art Set
description:
Learn to paint like the Masters! Recreate Sunflowers by Vincent van Gogh on real artist canvas. Illustrated instructions and and online tutorial teach young artists techniques used by the masters when creating their works of art. Showcase your artwork on the display easel when complete.

Complete set includes:

  • 6 in. w x 8 in. h printed canvas
  • pop-up easel, brush
  • 6 acrylic paint colors
  • number guide
  • fun facts
  • a hang tab to display your works of art
